Package realtimeweb.businesssearch.main

Interface Summary
AbstractBusinessSearch An abstract version of the Business Searchers.
Location An interface representing a Location.
 

Class Summary
BusinessCategory A business category is used to organize and filter related businesses.
BusinessQuery A query object used to make a search for businesses.
CoordinateLocation A Location that is given by a latitude and longitude.
NamedLocation A location specified primarily by an address - usually describing a larger area (such as "Blacksburg, VA").
RectangularLocation A RectangularLocation is a location specified by two latitude/longitude pairs.
 

Enum Summary
GeoAccuracy A GeoAccuracy specifies at what level a lat/long pair was found.
SortMode If the mode is BEST_MATCHED, a search may retrieve an additional 20 businesses past the initial limit of the first 20 results.
